window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There's no good way to prepare yourself to die....</b></p> <p>Guerro runs a kill team. They're good. Better than good. Or they were, until they walked into an ambush that wiped his team out and left Guerro for dead.&nbsp;</p> <p>All the evidence suggests they were betrayed, but by who, and why?&nbsp;</p> <p>Determined to avenge his team and settle old scores, Guerro embarks upon a one-man war, knowing that whoever put the kill order out on his people is still out there, watching for him to show his face so they can end him.&nbsp;</p> <p><b>A hard-biting SF thriller in the vein of </b><b><i>Blade Runner, Altered Carbon</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Titanborn</i></b><b>. </b></p> <p><b>Narrated by the award-winning R.C. Bray (</b><b><i>Galaxy's Edge, The Martian</i></b><b>)</b></p>"; 
